            <listitem>
                <para>
                    The OTRS website with source code, documentation and news is available at
<ulink url="https://www.otrs.com/">otrs.com/</ulink>.  Here you can also
find information about professional services and OTRS Administrator training
seminars from OTRS Group, the creator of OTRS.
                </para>
