        <varlistentry>
            <term>Fehler berichten</term>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    To report software defects, please visit <ulink
url="http://bugs.otrs.org/">http://bugs.otrs.org/</ulink> (see figure
below). Please take note of the difference between a bug and a configuration
issue. Configuration issues are problems that you encounter when setting a
system, or general questions regarding the use of OTRS. Bug reports should
only be used for issues with the source code of OTRS or other open source
OTRS modules itself. For configuration issues, you should either use the
<ulink url="https://www.otrs.com/solutions/">commercial support, available
from OTRS</ulink>, or the public mailing lists.
                </para>
                <para>
                    <figure>
                        <title>Fehlerverfolgungssystem</title>
<screenshot>
<graphic scale="40" fileref="screenshots/bugs-otrs-org.png"></graphic></screenshot></figure>
                </para>
